"Walang Diyos ang nakahanap ng iyong sakripisyo"

02:50:28.250 --> 02:50:33.208
“Pag-aalay ng mga pandama...”

02:50:33.375 --> 02:50:38.041
"Posible ba si Thinna?"

02:50:40.250 --> 02:50:45.500
<i>“Parang si Shaivam at Debosyon</i>
ay akin lang”

02:50:45.666 --> 02:50:50.875
"Aaham Brahma bilang ako"

02:50:51.083 --> 02:50:56.291
<i>"Nabuhay ako sa maling akala...</i>
Ang nakaraan ay nakaraan na..."

02:50:56.500 --> 02:51:01.583
"Ipinapasa ko sa iyo"

02:51:20.541 --> 02:51:24.375
"Shiva naadham Shiva vaadham
Shiva vedham Shiva modham"

02:51:24.583 --> 02:51:30.250
<i>“Iyo ba lahat</i>
ang ligaw na bata... Namaha”

02:51:32.750 --> 02:51:37.666
<i>“Shiva's seed Shivabhoojam</i>
Shiva bhojam Shiva raajam Shivathejam”

02:51:37.833 --> 02:51:42.791
“Ikaw ang aadivasi... Namaha”

02:51:44.750 --> 02:51:46.250
<i>“Shivagaathram (boses)</i>
Shivasthothram”

02:51:46.458 --> 02:51:48.041
<i>“Shiva Kshethram (Shrine)</i>
Shiva kshethram”

02:51:48.250 --> 02:51:50.833
"Shiva chatram Shiva gothram
Shiva soothram"

02:51:51.041 --> 02:51:53.458
<i>“Shiva Shiva Shiva</i>
Ang mata ni Shiva ay sa iyo lahat”

02:51:53.625 --> 02:51:58.125
“Hey moolavaasee... Relax”

02:52:11.083 --> 02:52:15.208
<i>"Deboto o deboto, ikaw ay</i>
isang tunay na deboto ng Shiva"

02:52:15.416 --> 02:52:19.791
<i>"Sa harap mo,</i>
kung gaano ako kamukha ng buhangin"

02:52:20.000 --> 02:52:23.000
“Hindi ba Mahabhakthaa”

02:52:23.208 --> 02:52:25.916
<i>"Hinati niya ang kanyang dibdib na Sinusukat</i>
gamit ang ruthiram"

02:52:26.125 --> 02:52:28.958
<i>"Tumayo ka sa pantay na sukat</i>
sa Panginoon Anjaneya"

02:52:29.166 --> 02:52:31.708
<i>"na nagpakita ng kanyang debosyon</i>
sa buong mundo"

02:52:31.875 --> 02:52:35.166
"ang nagdarasal kay Raghuraama"

02:52:35.375 --> 02:52:38.250
“Hoy... ang mata ni Shiva”

02:52:38.625 --> 02:52:39.750
“Ang yabang ng aking mga mata...”

02:52:39.958 --> 02:52:41.208
"Ipagmalaki mo ang aking pagmamataas"

02:52:41.416 --> 02:52:42.708
"Ipagmalaki mo ang aking kaluluwa..."

02:52:42.916 --> 02:52:44.291
"maging pride ko"

02:52:44.458 --> 02:52:47.500
"Ginawa mo ito bilang dharbha"

02:52:47.708 --> 02:52:48.791
“Hoy.. anak ng gubat”

